media-remove-metadata - Remove EXIF Metadata

USAGE:
    media-remove-metadata <file1> [file2] [file3] ...

DESCRIPTION:
    Remove all EXIF metadata from photo files using exiftool.

ARGUMENTS:
    file1, file2, file3...
        Photo files to process (at least one required)

EXAMPLES:
    media-remove-metadata photo.jpg
    media-remove-metadata *.jpg
    media-remove-metadata image1.jpg image2.jpg
